                  {
                    "cta": "Next!",
                    "text": "Hey! Today we will learn how to share technical updates at work.\nYou will learn to suggest approaches and give timelines to your team.",
                    "media": {
                      "url": "https://r2-activity-data.gosupernova.live/system-uploads/scenario-data/177aca95-66da-4ebe-8b84-447b526c6bed-Technical-update---3.jpg",
                      "type": "image"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "cta": "Got it!",
                    "text": "To suggest an approach with a timeline, say:\n\"I think we should [approach]. It'll take about [time].\"\nFor example: \"I think we should use a separate service for notifications. It'll take about two weeks.\"",
                    "media": {
                      "url": "https://r2-activity-data.gosupernova.live/system-uploads/scenario-data/177aca95-66da-4ebe-8b84-447b526c6bed-Technical-update---3.jpg",
                      "type": "image"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "cta": "Nice!",
                    "text": "To talk about finishing work by a deadline, say:\n\"If we [action], we can finish by [date].\"\nFor example: \"If we split the work, we can finish by end of March.\"",
                    "media": {
                      "url": "https://r2-activity-data.gosupernova.live/system-uploads/scenario-data/177aca95-66da-4ebe-8b84-447b526c6bed-Technical-update---3.jpg",
                      "type": "image"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "cta": "Makes sense!",
                    "text": "To give two choices to your team, say:\n\"We can either [option A] or [option B].\"\nFor example: \"We can either fix the current module or build a new one.\"",
                    "media": {
                      "url": "https://r2-activity-data.gosupernova.live/system-uploads/scenario-data/177aca95-66da-4ebe-8b84-447b526c6bed-Technical-update---3.jpg",
                      "type": "image"
                    }
                  },
